		<tr>
			<td><br><img src=/shared_files/techspeakers_photos/Scaglione_Bob.jpg align=left valign="top">&nbsp;Bob Scaglione serves as senior vice president and group manager for the Product and Marketing Group at Sharp.  He oversees marketing and product development for Sharp’s lineup of consumer and professional display products, consumer audio and video products, and appliances.<br><br>
Scaglione joined Sharp in 1989 as sales manager for Audio/Video products and also served as marketing manager for Televisions, national sales and merchandising manager for camcorders. He had also helped launch Sharp’s LCD and HDTV products while serving as the Associate VP of Sales and Marketing for the Digital Products Group.  Prior to joining Sharp he was a buyer for Abraham & Straus.<br><br>
Scaglione holds a B.S. in marketing from the University of Scranton. <br><br>
 



</td>
		
		
